# Dr. Frank Drake formulated and equation in 1961 not for the purpose of quantifying the number of civilizations 
# but as a way to simulate scientific dialogue at the first scientific meeting on the search for extraterrestrial intelligence (SETI)[1][2]
# This repository is meant to provide and R script which can be modified easy by future parties and easily visualize the equation.

